          "name": "Hypnotic Eye",
          "description": "Hypnotizes an enemy with the lowest TU and Mega Poisons them for 200TU. A Hypnotized enemy will use its next turn to grant the turn to and Purify the hypnotizer (the turn will be lost as if it were sleeping), and then the hypnosis will end.\n\nThis skill becomes locked for 90TU after use and cannot be used if an enemy is already Hypnotized or if there are less than 2 enemies on the battlefield. Hypnosis will fail against Boss units. Hypnosis is not a status effect and cannot be removed by Purify skills, but will be canceled if the user is defeated or leaves the battlefield.",
